29
00:03:23,199 --> 00:03:23,519
Ber.

30
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,280
Vypadá, že nespěcháte?

31
00:03:34,639 --> 00:03:35,699
Dneska jdu do školy...

32
00:03:35,700 --> 00:03:37,060
